		<item>
		<title>US Stocks Have Correction Risk in the Week Ahead</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en/analysis/market-news/us-stocks-correction-risk</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 20:44:22 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Market news & Insights]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Recent news]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[S&P 500]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.atfx.com/?p=44746</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[The S&#38;P 500 fell last week with another failure at the 6,000 level hinting at a possible correction.  SP 500 – Weekly Chart  The S&#38;P 500 has fallen to close at 5,827 and opens up the potential for a further correction toward the 5,000 level.  The US December jobs report revealed a drop in the [&#8230;]]]></description>
